configuration.Query:
select id,
Borough,
`ZIP.CODE`,
LATITUDE,
LONGITUDE,
LOCATION,
`ON.STREET.NAME`,
`CROSS.STREET.NAME`,
`OFF.STREET.NAME`,
`Persons injured`,
`Persons killed`,
`Pedestrians injured` as Pedestrians_injured,
`Pedestrians killed` as Pedestrians_killed,
`Cyclist injured` as Cyclist_injured,
`Cyclist killed` as Cyclist_killed,
`Motorist injured` as Motorist_injured,
`Motorist killed` as Motorist_killed,
`CONTRIBUTING.FACTOR.VEHICLE.1`,
`CONTRIBUTING.FACTOR.VEHICLE.2`,
`CONTRIBUTING.FACTOR.VEHICLE.3`,
`CONTRIBUTING.FACTOR.VEHICLE.4`,
`CONTRIBUTING.FACTOR.VEHICLE.5`,
`UNIQUE.KEY`,
`Vehicle type1`,
`Vehicle type2`,
`Vehicle type3`,
`Vehicle type4`,
`Vehicle type5`,
datetime,
location2,
`Number accidents`, 
CONCAT(UCASE(LEFT(Borough, 1)), 
                             LCASE(SUBSTRING(Borough, 2))) as borough_ass
from accidents_nyc
where CRC32(id) % 30 = 0 and extract(MONTH from datetime)='6'
